 <title>Managing Block Storage using Ceph</title>
 <para>
  Ceph is an open source, scalable, software-defined storage (SDS) platform
  that provides block and object storage with unified management.
 </para>
 <para>
  The &kw-hos-phrase; Ceph storage solution provides an unified, scalable, and
  stable storage solution for the management of the &kw-hos; volume storage
  (Cinder persistent volumes) service.
 </para>
